      "items": [
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "1",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 1:1"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "1",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Paul, and Silvanus, and Timotheus, unto the church of the Thessalonians ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.1",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "which is",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.1.1",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.1.1"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " in God the Father and ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.1",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "in",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.1.1",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.1.1"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " the Lord Jesus Christ: Grace ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.1",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "be",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.1.1",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.1.1"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " unto you, and peace, from God our Father, and the Lord Jesus Christ. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.1",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.1"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "2",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 1:2"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "2",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "We give thanks to God always for you all, making mention of you in our prayers; ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.2",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.2"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "3",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 1:3"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "3",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Remembering without ceasing your work of faith, and labour of love, and patience of hope in our Lord Jesus Christ, in the sight of God and our Father; ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.3",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.3"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "4",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 1:4"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "4",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "Knowing, brethren beloved, your election of God. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.4",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.4"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "5",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 1:5"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "5",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For our gospel came not unto you in word only, but also in power, and in the Holy Ghost, and in much assurance; as ye know what manner of men we were among you for your sake. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.5",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.5"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "6",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 1:6"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "6",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And ye became followers of us, and of the Lord, having received the word in much affliction, with joy of the Holy Ghost: ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.6",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.6"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "7",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 1:7"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "7",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "So that ye were ensamples to all that believe in Macedonia and Achaia. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.7",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.7"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "8",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 1:8"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "8",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For from you sounded out the word of the Lord not only in Macedonia and Achaia, but also in every place your faith to God-ward is spread abroad; so that we need not to speak any thing. ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.8",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.8"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "9",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 1:9"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "9",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "For they themselves shew of us what manner of entering in we had unto you, and how ye turned to God from idols to serve the living and true God; ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.9",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.9"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "verse",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "number": "10",
            "style": "v",
            "sid": "1TH 1:10"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "10",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "And to wait for his Son from heaven, whom he raised from the dead, ",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.10",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.10"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "char",
          "type": "tag",
          "attrs": {
            "style": "add"
          },
          "items": [
            {
              "text": "even",
              "type": "text",
              "attrs": {
                "verseId": "1TH.1.10",
                "verseOrgIds": [
                  "1TH.1.10"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " Jesus, which delivered us from the wrath to come.",
          "type": "text",
          "attrs": {
            "verseId": "1TH.1.10",
            "verseOrgIds": [
              "1TH.1.10"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
